Hi everyone!

After 9 successive losses I have finally managed to win a game.  In mitigation, most of the losses were against 2000+ oppo!  This victory came against my buddy dmaestro.  He seemed to have a slight edge in the middlegame but somehow, after a late tactical melee he ended up dropping the exchange as a result of a pin.  This game is another Latvian.  I kick off with the standard e4 and my opponent responds with the equally standard e5.  Another standard Nf3 follows and then ......
